<t>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Food;</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Ingredient WHERE category = 'Vegetable';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Ingredient WHERE category = 'Vegetable';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT id, name, category FROM Food WHERE category = 'Fruit';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);</t><s>select id, name, category from food where category = 'fruit';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Beverage WHERE brand = 'Coca-Cola';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);</t><s>SELECT name, type, price FROM Menu WHERE type = 'Dinner';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT name, type, price FROM Menu WHERE type = 'Dinner';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>select id, name from recipe where name like '%cake%';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT name, description FROM Recipe WHERE name != 'Pasta';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Ingredient WHERE category = 'Spice';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>select * from ingredient where category = 'spice';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);</t><s>SELECT id, name, price FROM Food ORDER BY price DESC;</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>select id, name, price from food order by price desc;</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT id, name, price FROM Food ORDER BY price DESC;</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Beverage WHERE price = (SELECT MAX(price) FROM Beverage);</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Beverage WHERE price = (SELECT MAX(price) FROM Beverage);</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);</t><s>select name, type, price from menu where name like '%salad%';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);</t><s>SELECT name, type, price FROM Menu WHERE name LIKE '%Salad%';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Food (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2), quantity INT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Menu (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), type VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Beverage (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), brand VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>select * from recipe where description like '%chicken%';</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Recipe (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS Ingredient (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), category VARCHAR(255), price DECIMAL(10, 2);</t><s>SELECT * FROM Recipe WHERE description LIKE '%chicken%';</s>
